item.title: Estes body tubes
item.description: Every time I'm starting a new rocket design, I find myself opening google and looking for the exact dimensions of each estes body tube. I decided to put together the values in a table for easy access. I took this values from the Estes webpage: Name ID OD Wall Length BT-5 13.2mm 13.8mm 0.3mm 457mm BT-20 18mm 18.7mm 0.35mm 457mm BT-50 24.
